description: lips sealed or open book? fox or owl? on the set of our fall 2015 campaign shoot, we sat and indulged in some very telling small talk with our cast of interesting characters including Karlie Koss, Alice Smith, Jon Batiste, Anh Duong, Karley Sciortino, and Alireza Niroomand. listen in.
